data.title: Send technical support request
data.text:
In matters concerning registration confirmation and new password emails, wait for half an hour. Sometimes email is slow going through all spam filters.

In matters concerning new password emails, note that for security reasons the system does not tell you if the username exists. Try registering yourself before sending a technical support request.
